WEBVTT

00:03:58.924 --> 00:04:03.004
but also getting our faces black,
while experimenting with this pollution.

00:04:07.208 --> 00:04:10.854
From last year onwards, we started 
fixing these weird instruments

00:04:10.854 --> 00:04:15.224
onto cars and bringing them on the roads
in Bangalore to collect pollution.

00:04:15.248 --> 00:04:18.384
This is a device that captures
the smoke produced by the car

00:04:18.408 --> 00:04:22.384
and blocks those particles without 
putting any mechanical pressure.

00:04:22.408 --> 00:04:25.384
The particles are somewhat like this.

00:04:25.408 --> 00:04:29.704
They are currently present in your lungs
because of your breathing.

00:04:29.728 --> 00:04:33.304
Their size is measured in nano microns.